high_descs: Turn left and walk to the white container on the floor next to the fridge on the left.
Pick up the potato from inside the white container.
Turn around and walk to the white stove on the right.
Put the potato inside the microwave, heat it for a few seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on the left.
Put the heated potato on the counter to the left of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn left at the trash bin between the sink and the fridge, go to the trash bin.
Take a potato from the trash bin.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to the oven, go forward to the oven.
Cook the potato in the microwave above the oven. Take the potato from the microwave.
Go to the right to the counter to the right of the oven.
Put the potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go toward the door, then turn left to face the trash bin next to the fridge.
Take the potato from the trash bin.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to go towards the stove, and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside and heat it up, then take it out.
Move to your right to go to the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Place the potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato on the counter.
